<plot>In the middle of the desert, a solitary woman has car trouble as the radio reports a series of killings in the area. A red SUV stops and a man, dressed in a string tie and a black Western suit, offers to help. She's sassy rather than appreciative. He takes out a cell phone to call a tow, but there's no service. She turns her back to him and reaches inside for a cigarette. Are sparks about to fly?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?074032</url></doc>
